20DC%2C%20which%20has%20been%20the%20home%20to%20three%20giant%20pandas%20for%2050%20years%2C%20will%20soon%20send%20them%20back%20to%20China.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20pandas%20are%20set%20to%20return%20in%20December%20this%20year%20following%20the%20end%20of%20a%20three-year-long%20agreement%20with%20China's%20wildlife%20agency%2C%20reported%20Bloomberg.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20ones%20in%20Washington%20DC%20gone%2C%20only%20four%20giant%20pandas%20will%20remain%20in%20the%20Atalanta%20Zoo%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20shift%20back%20by%20next%20year%2C%20unless%20both%20countries%20strike%20a%20new%20deal%20among%20themselves%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChee%20Meng%20Tan%2C%20who%20is%20an%20associate%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Nottingham%20in%20Malaysia%20and%20studies%20panda%20diplomacy%2C%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2F09%2F28%2Fpandas-returning-china-dc-zoo%2F%5C%22%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20perhaps%20Beijing's%20way%20of%20signalling%20to%20the%20West%20that%20they%20may%20not%20be%20very%20happy%20with%20how%20things%20are%20going.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20may%20be%20one%20way%20of%20telling%20people%20that%20you're%20not%20treating%20us%20very%20well%2C%20so%20maybe%20we'll%20pull%20out%20our%20pandas.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%20this%2C%20the%20pandas%20from%20San%20Diego%20and%20Memphis%20had%20left%20in%202019%20and%20April%202023%2C%20respectively%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20instance%20of%20China's%20Panda%20Diplomacy%20can%20be%20dated%20back%20to%201941%20but%20it%20wasn't%20until%20President%20Nixon%20visited%20China%20in%201972%20that%20the%20US%20were%20rewarded%20with%20any.%20After%20his%20visit%2C%20the%20US%20were%20gifted%20two%20pandas%20which%20were%20kept%20at%20the%20National%20Zoo%20in%20Washington%20DC%2C%20the%20report%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20beyond%20political%20motives%2C%20the%20pandas%20%E2%80%93%20named%20Mei%20Xiang%20and%20Tian%20Tian%20%E2%80%93%20have%20also%20served%20the%20purpose%20of%20entertainment.%20Recently%2C%20their%203-year-old%20male%20cub%2C%20Xiao%20Qi%20Ji%20had%20also%20become%20a%20centre%20of%20attraction%20for%20the%20crowd%20of%20the%20zoo.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%20Some%20experts%20have%20also%20suggested%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20send%20back%20the%20pandas%20might%20not%20be%20solely%20political%20reasons.%20They%20have%20risen%20to%20the%20point%20that%20pandas%20are%20no%20longer%20under%20the%20classification%20of%20%E2%80%98Endangered%20Species'.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20they%20feel%2C%20China%20is%20trying%20to%20establish%20their%20network%20of%20national%20parks%20and%20sanctuary.%20This%20may%20have%20added%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20do%20not%20need%20to%20send%20the%20pandas%20abroad%20anymore%20to%20conserve%20and%20breed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696043640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F3fe07d04_panda-generic_625x300_30_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffor-the-first-time-in-50-years-us-wont-have-any-panda-heres-why-4435386%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20all%20panda%20lovers%20in%20the%20US%2C%20there%20is%20sad%20news.%20The%20National%20Zoo%2C%20in%20Washington%20DC%2C%20which%20has%20been%20the%20home%20to%20three%20giant%20pandas%20for%2050%20years%2C%20will%20soon%20send%20them%20back%20to%20China.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffor-the-first-time-in-50-years-us-wont-have-any-panda-heres-why-4435386%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffor-the-first-time-in-50-years-us-w