rst%20Evidence%20Of%20Black%20Hole%20Spinning%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAstronomers%20have%20found%20the%20first%20direct%20evidence%20of%20a%20black%20hole%20spinning.%20The%20observations%20provide%20new%20insights%20into%20the%20enigmatic%20celestial%20object%20and%20focus%20on%20the%20supermassive%20black%20hole%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20neighbouring%20Messier%2087%20(M87)%20galaxy.%20On%20the%20lines%20of%20other%20supermassive%20black%20holes%2C%20M87%2C%20too%2C%20features%20powerful%20jets%20launched%20from%20the%20poles%20at%20close%20to%20the%20speed%20of%20light%20into%20intergalactic%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EScientists%20believe%20the%20rotation%20of%20a%20black%20hole%20powers%20these%20cosmic%20jets%2C%20but%20until%20now%20there%20was%20no%20direct%20evidence.%20The%20black%20hole%20has%20been%20imaged%20by%20Event%20Horizon%20Telescope%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fscience%2F2023%2Fapr%2F26%2Fastronomers-capture-first-image-of-jet-being-launched-from-edge-of-black-hole%5C%22%3EThe%20Guardian%20%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Ru-Sen%20Lu%2C%20the%20lead%20author%20of%20the%20Shanghai%20Astronomical%20Observatory%2C%20said%20that%20the%20scientific%20community%20knows%20jets%20are%20ejected%20from%20the%20region%20surrounding%20black%20holes.%20%26quot%3BBut%20we%20still%20do%20not%20fully%20understand%20how%20this%20happens%2C%26quot%3B%20Lu%20said%2C%20adding%20that%2C%20they%20needed%20to%20observe%20the%20origin%20of%20the%20jet%20as%20close%20as%20possible%20to%20the%20black%20hole.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EM87%2C%20located%2055%20million%20light%20years%20from%20the%20Earth%2C%20harbours%20a%20black%20hole%206.5%20billion%20times%20more%20massive%20than%20the%20Sun.%20Beyond%20the%20black%20hole%20is%20an%20accretion%20disk%20of%20gas%20and%20dust%20swirling%20on%20the%20precipice%20of%20the%20cosmic%20sinkhole.%20Some%20of%20this%20material%2C%20as%20per%20the%20scientists%2C%20will%20fall%20into%20the%20black%20hole%20and%20disappear%20forever.%20However%2C%20a%20small%20fraction%20will%20be%20ejected%20out%20from%20the%20poles%20of%20the%20black%20hole%20at%20more%20than%2099.99%25%20of%20the%20speed%20of%20light.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EResearch%2C%20published%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41586-023-06479-6.epdf%3Fsharing_token%3DDUYbilhBNZCoW2G_l5pA4NRgN0jAjWel9jnR3ZoTv0PJ9TSvKVXAu99JIrtZXr4kP9t9OXFLc5htg6TE0uK0DAlo3acv1ev2vg7AC8OWQLgKXMBcOqpZtflNO9IhCxSEzZLZnVahSFtbSOT-dBEWMW6wwKsvb8zAGjGrnvWDewqXzvHwoX1FjaEZ7ATUc4pHRgrHERgZ04V_9vXN8s-jz0kXk0S6tE8gh08Tu2pXtB18C9_rMAOPWD3Tvsv4cj14FWLzdGQr8tJnFGKD9rtncSU0cmhmFje-ms6iWYp5dRXFzvlyl5QyQaqA4d-1j9xzNOQhW6NuViE3mZ86WmiVRQ%253D%253D%26tracking_referrer%3Dwww.theguardian.com%5C%22%3ENature%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20used%20observations%20of%20M87%20from%20a%20global%20network%20of%20radio%20telescopes%20from%202000%20to%202022.%20Scientists%20noticed%20a%20recurring%2011-year%20cycle%20in%20the%20jet%2C%20which%20was%20found%20to%20precess%20around%20a%20central%20point%20at%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20black%20hole.%20It%20indicated%20a%20misalignment%20between%20the%20black%20hole's%20spin%20axis%20and%20the%20accretion%20disk%2C%20leading%20the%20jet%20to%20move%20like%20a%20spinning%20top.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20picture%20of%20a%20black%20hole%20was%20obtained%20back%20in%202019%2C%20according%20to%20US%20space%20agency%20NASA.%20The%20supermassive%20black%20hole%2C%20imaged%20by%20the%20Event%20Horizon%20Telescope%2C%20was%20said%20to%20be%20located%20in%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20elliptical%20galaxy%20M87%2C%20located%20about%2055%20million%20light-years%20from%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20a%20Black%20Hole%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENASA%20describes%20a%20black%20hole%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdense%2C%20compact%20object%20whose%20gravitational%20pull%20is%20so%20strong%20(to%20a%20certain%20distance)%20that%20nothing%20can%20escape%2C%20not%20even%20light.%E2%80%9D%20It%20is%20said%20that%20black%20holes%20are%20formed%20when%20massive%20stars%20collapse%20at%20the%20ends%20of%20their%20evolution.%20The%20gravity%20is%20extremely%20strong%20because%20matter%20(the%20mass)%20has%20been%20squeezed%20into%20a%20tiny%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696041780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fefaplj4o_black-hole_625x300_12_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fscientists-confirm-first-evidence-of-black-hole-spinning-4435720%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Astronomers%20have%20found%20the%20first%20direct%20evidence%20of%20a%20black%20hole%20spinning.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fscientists-confirm-first-evidence-of-black-hole-spinning-4435720%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fscientists-confirm-first-evidence-of-black-hole-spinning-4435720%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fscientists-confirm-first-evidence-of-black-hole-spinning-4435720%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kartik%20wraps%20up%20Chandu%20Champion%20shoot%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696041726000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104056296%2Cimgsize-29228.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkartik-aaryan-wraps-up-power-packed-shoot-of-chandu-champion-enjoys-ice-bath-in-kashmir%2Farticleshow%2F104056271.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104056271.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EActor%20Kartik%20Aaryan%20celebrated%20wrapping%20up%20the%20action%20schedule%20of%20his%20film%20'Chandu%20Champion'%20by%20taking%20an%20ice%20bath%20in%20a%20river%20in%20Kashmir.%20He%20shared%20a%20video%20of%20himself%20soaking%20in%20the%20cold%20stream%20on%20Instagram.%20'Chandu%20Champion'%2C%20directed%20by%20Kabir%20Khan%2C%20is%20based%20on%20a%20real-life%20sports%20story%20and%20is%20set%20to%20release%20on%20June%2014%2C%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Getting%20Away%20With%20Murder%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F29175202%2Fmodi-biden-trudeau.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202022%2C%20the%20Israelis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2F2022%2F5%2F11%2F23067365%2Fshireen-abu-akleh-palestinian-journalist-killed-israel%5C%22%3Emurdered%20Shireen%20Abu%20Akleh%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20an%20American%20citizen%20and%20a%20journalist%20clearly%20wearing%20a%20vest%20that%20marked%20her%20as%20so%2C%20a%20significant%20distance%20away%20from%20where%20a%20firefight%20was%20happening.%20Four%20years%20earlier%2C%20in%20October%202018%2C%20the%20Saudis%20murdered%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-45812399%5C%22%3EJamal%20Khashoggi%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20who%20held%20a%20US%20green%20card%20and%20was%20a%20columnist%20for%20the%20%3Cem%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20in%20Turkey%2C%20a%20NATO%20ally.%20Today%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20foreign%20policy%20issues%20being%20pursued%20by%20the%20US%20administration%20is%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.al-monitor.com%2Foriginals%2F2023%2F09%2Fisrael-saudi-arabia-see-progress-ties-iran-sounds-warning%5C%22%3EIsrael-Saudi%20rapprochement%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20wondering%20what%20will%20happen%20after%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20very%20public%20allegation%20of%20Indian%20involvement%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhardeep-singh-nijjar-killing-khalistan-speculation%5C%22%3EHardeep%20Sing%20Nijjar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20this%20is%20one%20possible%20pathway.%20Of%20course%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20himself%20has%20a%20very%20personal%20experience%20on%20how%20to%20get%20away%20with%20murder.%20And%20the%20announcement%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2023%2F09%2F11%2Fmiddleeast%2Fus-india-gulf-europe-corridor-mime-intl%2Findex.html%5C%22%3Ethe%20trade%20route%3C%2Fa%3E%20connecting%20India%2C%20the%20UAE%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20and%20Israel%20with%20Europe%20at%20the%20G20%20summit%20%E2%80%93%20after%20Canada%20would%20have%20shared%20intelligence%20with%20the%20US%20on%20the%20murder%20of%20Nijjar%20%E2%80%93%20is%20an%20important%20indicator%20of%20how%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20will%20deal%20with%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdvocates%20of%20Henry%20Kissinger-style%20foreign%20policy%20would%20have%20it%20no%20other%20way.%20In%20their%20worldview%2C%20what%20matters%20is%20whether%20a%20state%20is%20an%20ally%20or%20an%20enemy.%20But%20an%20ally%20can%20also%20be%20more%20costly%20than%20they%20are%20worth%2C%20as%20Kissinger%20found%20out.%20Kissinger%2C%20as%20the%20Secretary%20of%20State%20under%20US%20President%20Richard%20Nixon%2C%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2023%2F09%2F10%2F1193755188%2Fchile-coup-50-years-pinochet-kissinger-human-rights-allende%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cthe%20dominant%20policymaker%20on%20Chile%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20involved%20destabilising%20the%20elected%20Chilean%20government%20under%20Salvador%20Allende%20and%20encouraging%20a%20military%20coup%20in%201973.%20Despite%20the%20atrocities%20that%20ensued%2C%20the%20US%20turned%20a%20blind%20eye.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20in%201976%2C%20Chilean%20agents%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdcist.com%2Fstory%2F16%2F09%2F21%2Fletelier%2F%5C%22%3Eassassinated%20a%20dissident%20in%20Washington%20DC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20capital%20of%20the%20US%2C%20using%20a%20car%20bomb.%20This%20was%20the%20same%20year%20that%20Nixon%20resigned%20while%20facing%20impeachment%2C%20taking%20Kissinger%20with%20him.%20Due%20to%20the%20activities%20of%20the%20educated%20Chilean%20diaspora%20highlighting%20the%20atrocities%20under%20General%20Augusto%20Pinochet%20and%20Chilean%20acts%20of%20terrorism%20on%20US%20soil%2C%20there%20was%20a%20strong%20pushback%20by%20civil%20society%20and%20the%20US%20Congress%20against%20the%20US%20presidency%20and%20intelligence%20services.%20Jimmy%20Carter%2C%20who%20was%20elected%20in%201979%2C%20imposed%20sanctions%20against%20Chile%20in%201979.%20And%20even%20when%20Ronald%20Reagan%20%E2%80%93%20often%20seen%20as%20the%20ultimate%20US%20Cold%20War%20president%20%E2%80%93%20came%20to%20power%2C%20they%20stayed%2C%20even%20if%20Pinochet%20continued%20to%20rule%20until%201988%2C%20almost%20until%20the%20end%20of%20the%20Cold%20War.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20of%20the%20US%20and%20Pinochet%20is%20particularly%20relevant%20as%20the%20US-China%20rivalry%20continues%20to%20heighten.%20India%20is%20a%20key%20player%20in%20this%20game%2C%20one%20that%20the%20US-led%20allies%20want%20on%20their%20side%2C%20so%20they%20will%20hold%20their%20noses%20and%20smile%20for%20the%20cameras.%20If%20Biden%20can%20go%20from%20calling%20Mohammad%20bin%20Salman%20%E2%80%93%20the%20crown%20prince%20of%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20allegedly%20key%20architect%20of%20Khashoggi%E2%80%99s%20murder%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.commondreams.org%2Fnews%2F2022%2F07%2F15%2Fbone-saw-pariah-fist-bump-outrage-biden-greets-murderous-saudi-prince%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CMr%20Bone%20Saw%E2%80%9D%20to%20giving%20him%20a%20fist%20bump%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20surely%20the%20same%20applies%20to%20India%3F%20As%20it%20is%2C%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20have%20a%20history%20of%20whitewashing%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20involvement%20in%20such%20crimes.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20are%20important%20risks%20for%20the%20Biden%20administration%20in%20pursuing%20this%20line%20of%20action%20%E2%80%93%20possibly%20why%20the%20US%20administration%20has%20gone%20out%20of%20its%20way%20to%20say%20there%20are%20no%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnijjar-killing-us-canada-no-special-exemption%5C%22%3Especial%20exemptions%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20countries%20to%20carry%20out%20targeted%20killings%20on%20foreign%20soil.%20The%20US%20will%20be%20aware%20that%20a%20closer%20engagement%20with%20leaders%20with%20terrible%20reputations%20%E2%80%93%20such%20as%20Saudi%20under%20Mohammad%20bin%20Salman%2C%20India%20under%20Modi%2C%20and%20Israel%20under%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20%E2%80%93%20makes%20a%20mockery%20of%20the%20idea%20that%20the%20fight%20against%20China%20and%20its%20allies%20is%20about%20the%20%E2%80%98defence%20of%20democracy%E2%80%99.%20For%20China%2C%20Russia%2C%20and%20Iran%20%E2%80%93%20among%20others%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Canada-India%20diplomatic%20crisis%20is%20a%20windfall.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20another%20issue%20in%20the%20Nijjar%20killing%20that%20makes%20it%20different%20from%20that%20of%20Abu%20Akleh%20and%20Khashoggi%20%E2%80%93%20it%20happened%20on%20the%20soil%20of%20a%20developed%20country.%20The%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20%E2%80%93%20Europe%2C%20Australia%2C%20Canada%20and%20New%20Zealand%2C%20will%20find%20this%20hard%20to%20swallow%20because%20it%20follows%20the%20China-Russia%20playbook.%20Both%20of%20these%20countries%20have%20regularly%20poured%20vitriol%20on%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20for%20hosting%20people%20that%20China%20and%20Russia%20identify%20as%20%E2%80%9Csplittists%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cterrorists%E2%80%9D.%20Often%20these%20are%20vulnerable%20minorities%20who%20have%20faced%20persecution%2C%20such%20as%20Tibetans%2C%20Uyghurs%2C%20and%20Chechens.%20Sikhs%20who%20are%20non-violent%20proponents%20of%20the%20Khalistan%20cause%20%E2%80%93%20however%20India%20defines%20it%20%E2%80%93%20would%20fit%20perfectly%20into%20this%20set%20of%20people.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20576px)%2085vw%2C%20576px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19140300%2FF6XA2MyWQAAYBoQ.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22576%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19140300%2FF6XA2MyWQAAYBoQ.jpeg%20576w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19140300%2FF6XA2MyWQAAYBoQ-300x225.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-673704%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22432%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EHardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20supporters.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40CitizenAnkit%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Indian%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%2C%20instead%20of%20engaging%20with%20the%20investigation%20into%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20killing%2C%20attempts%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2023%2F09%2F22%2Findia%2Findia-canada-sikh-activist-row-friday-intl-hnk%2Findex.html%5C%22%3Ereframe%20the%20conversation%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20Canada%20%E2%80%9Cas%20a%20safe%20haven%20for%20terrorists%2C%20for%20extremists%2C%20and%20for%20organised%20crime%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20only%20echoes%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voanews.com%2Fa%2Fchina-protests-us-meeting-with-dalai-lama-in-india-%2F7175454.html%5C%22%3EChinese%20language%20on%20Tibetans%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Accepting%20that%20India%20has%20a%20right%20to%20carry%20out%20extra-territorial%20activity%20on%20their%20soil%20to%20act%20against%20such%20groups%20would%20also%20be%20an%20opening%20to%20China%20and%20Russia%2C%20as%20well%20as%20any%20other%20country%20that%20would%20like%20to%20do%20so.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20long%20been%20accused%20of%20using%20its%20diaspora%20and%20diplomatic%20corps%20as%20cover%20to%20pursue%20action%20against%20dissidents%20abroad.%20There%20are%20even%20reports%20of%20informal%20Chinese%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2022%2F12%2F04%2Fworld%2Fchina-overseas-police-stations-intl-cmd%2Findex.html%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98police%20stations%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20the%20world.%20Russia%2C%20of%20course%2C%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.buzzfeednews.com%2Farticle%2Fheidiblake%2Fputin-global-assassination-campaign-berezovsky-london%5C%22%3Eassassinating%20dissidents%3C%2Fa%3E%20globally.%20If%20India%20is%20allowed%20to%20act%20against%20%E2%80%9Cterrorists%E2%80%9D%20abroad%20in%20places%20where%20the%20host%20countries%20give%20them%20refuge%2C%20then%20Russia%20would%20feel%20perfectly%20in%20the%20right%20to%20do%20things%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fgermany-russian-man-guilty-of-chechen-dissident-murder-plot%2Fa-66683185%5C%22%3Emurder%20dissidents%20in%20Germany%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20may%20well%20be%20right%2C%20and%20the%20Canadian%20investigation%20may%20be%20fraught%20with%20errors.%20Only%20a%20transparent%20and%20credible%20investigation%20will%20put%20such%20rumours%20to%20rest.%20But%20right%20now%2C%20it%20is%20choosing%20the%20language%20of%20China%20and%20Russia%20in%20responding%20to%20the%20Canadian%20allegations.%20At%20some%20point%2C%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20will%20have%20to%20ask%20themselves%20if%20that%20is%20what%20they%20want%20from%20a%20potential%20ally.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fomair-ahmad%5C%22%3EOmair%20Ahmad%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20author%20and%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696041045000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2