011%20World%20Cup%20hero%20Yuvraj%20Singh.%20All-rounder%20Axar%20Patel%20was%20ruled%20out%20of%20the%20global%20event%20due%20to%20quadriceps%20tear%20and%20the%20management%20replaced%20him%20with%20senior%20off-spinner%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin.%20Ashwin%20was%20summoned%20for%20the%20ODI%20series%20against%20Australia%20and%20eventually%20he%20was%20included%20in%20the%20final%2015-man%20squad%20as%20Chahal%20and%20Washington%20miss%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20personally%20feel%20the%20only%20miss%20in%20this%20side%20is%20Yuzvendra%20Chahal.%20I%20think%20the%20only%20aspect%20that%20is%20missing%20from%20this%20team%20is%20a%20leg-spinner%2C%26quot%3B%20Yuvraj%20told%20PTI%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20very%20keen%20to%20see%20Washington%20Sundar%20in%20the%20side%20if%20we%20are%20not%20picking%20up%20Yuzi.%20But%20maybe%20the%20team%20wanted%20an%20experienced%20bowler%2C%20so%20that%20is%20why%20I%20think%20they%20went%20with%20R%20Ashwin%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20of%20India's%20greatest%20ODI%20cricketers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYuvraj%20spoke%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20an%20event%2C%20organised%20by%20Vicks%2C%20to%20release%20the%20World%20Cup%20anthem.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20performance%20of%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20will%20have%20a%20massive%20bearing%20on%20India's%20campaign%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20at%20home%2C%20felt%20former%20India%20batter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBumrah%20returned%20to%20the%20Indian%20side%20during%20the%20T20I%20series%20against%20Ireland%20recently%20after%20a%20long%20injury%20lay-off%20and%20he%20also%20produced%20intense%20efforts%20in%20the%20Asia%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJasprit%20is%20a%20match-winner%2C%20like%20Zak%20(Zaheer%20Khan)%20did%20for%20us%20back%20in%202011.%20What%20makes%20Jasprit%20a%20threat%20is%20he%20has%20skill%20and%20pace.%20He%20is%20an%20asset%20to%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20make%20a%20comeback%20from%20the%20back%20injury%20at%20this%20stage%20is%20quite%20big%20too.%20As%20a%20team%20you%20feel%20confident%20to%20have%20bowlers%20like%20that%2C%20they%20win%20you%20matches%20from%20any%20situation.%26quot%3B%20Yuvraj%2C%20who%20was%20the%20player%20of%20the%20tournament%20during%20the%202011%20World%20Cup%2C%20was%20pleased%20to%20see%20the%20growing%20maturity%20of%20Bumrah%20as%20a%20cricketer.%20%26quot%3BBumrah%20has%20matured%20in%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20he%20has%20captained%20India%20and%20has%20become%20a%20smart%20bowler.%20Rohit%20knows%20how%20to%20use%20him%20wisely%2C%20especially%20because%20he%20has%20captained%20Bumrah%20in%20the%20Mumbai%20Indians%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Yuvraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20advantage%20with%20Bumrah%20is%20that%20initially%20he%20can%20get%20wickets%20with%20pace%20but%20when%20he%20starts%20going%20for%20runs%2C%20his%20skillset%20will%20come%20into%20play.%20There%20will%20be%20days%20when%20you%20will%20win%20a%20game%20after%20scoring%20300%20or%20350-plus%20but%20these%20kinds%20of%20bowlers%20like%20Bumrah%20are%20needed%20to%20defend%20scores%20like%20250s%20and%20260s%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%2041-year-old%20was%20also%20chuffed%20to%20see%20the%20form%20of%20India's%20middle-order%20batters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20good%20thing%20that%20all%20our%20middle-order%20batters%20%E2%80%93%20KL%20(Rahul)%2C%20Ishan%20(Kishan)%20and%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20%E2%80%93%20are%20in%20good%20form.%20But%20the%20team%20management%20needs%20to%20decide%20the%2011%20and%20combination%20ahead%20of%20the%20tournament%20that%20will%20give%20the%20team%20a%20settled%20look%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYuvraj%20knows%20a%20thing%20or%20two%20about%20winning%20the%20World%20Cup%20as%20he%20was%20a%20part%20of%20India's%20triumphant%20sides%20in%202007%20(T20%20WC)%20and%202011%20(50-over%20WC).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20India%20had%20started%20their%20preparation%20for%20the%202011%20World%20Cup%20the%20moment%20Gary%20Kirsten%20joined%20the%20team%20as%20the%20head%20coach.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20started%20planning%20for%20the%20World%20Cup%20from%20the%20day%20Gary%20came%20on%20board.%20The%20first%20step%20was%20to%20get%20to%20the%20No.%201%20ranking%20in%20all%20formats%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20it%20is%20ODI%20cricket%20or%20Tests.%20When%20the%20World%20Cup%20came%2C%20we%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20players%20who%20were%20at%20the%20peak%20of%20their%20careers.%20The%20younger%20generation%20too%20had%20matured.%20So%2C%20it%20became%20a%20complete%20team%20effort%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20personal%20front%2C%20Yuvraj%20was%20battling%20injuries%20and%20other%20health%20issues%2C%20which%20was%20later%20diagnosed%20as%20cancer%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%202011%20big%20bash.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20how%20did%20he%20manage%20to%20rise%20above%20those%20obstacles%3F%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20battling%20injuries%20ahead%20of%20the%20World%20Cup%E2%80%A6neck%2C%20fingers%E2%80%A6and%20other%20health-related%20issues%20as%20I%20was%20not%20able%20to%20breathe%20properly.%20I%20had%20to%20put%20aside%20all%20of%20those%20things%20and%20concentrate%20on%20one%20goal%2C%20which%20is%20the%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20were%20playing%20in%20a%20physical%20state%20like%20that%2C%20you%20had%20to%20put%20the%20body%20on%20the%20line.%20I%20think%20to%20win%20a%20World%20Cup%20after%2028%20years%2C%20an%20effort%20like%20that%20was%20needed.%26quot%3B%20India%20had%20then%20won%20a%2050-over%20World%20Cup%2C%20their%20second%2C%20after%20a%20gap%20of%20nearly%20three%20decades%2C%20and%20Yuvraj%20hoped%20that%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20his%20bunch%20would%20end%20India's%2012-year%20wait%20for%20a%20third%20trophy%20at%20home%20next%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20love%20these%20guys%20as%20I%20get%20along%20with%20every%20one%20of%20them%20and%20I%20have%20also%20played%20with%20some%20of%20them.%20I%20feel%20that%20Virat%20and%20Rohit%20deserve%20a%20World%20Cup.%20So%2C%20everyone%20needs%20to%20put%20their%20body%20on%20the%20line%20for%20such%20a%20big%20stage%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYuvraj%20also%20advised%20the%20present%20bunch%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20distractions%20during%20the%20World%20Cup.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20tell%20them%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20distractions%20for%20the%20next%2040%20or%2045%20days%E2%80%A6media%2C%20friends%20and%20everything.%20They%20need%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20game%20exclusively.%20Sachin%20paaji%20(Tendulkar)%20used%20to%20tell%20us%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20signed%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696035360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F5o1kd78g_ravichandran-ashwin-bcci_625x300_10_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fchahal-or-washington-could-have-been-picked-as-axars-replacement-yuvraj-singh-4435076%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20was%20summoned%20for%20the%20ODI%20series%20against%20Australia%20and%20eventually%20he%20was%20included%20in%20the%20final%2015-man%20squad%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A366%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fchahal-or-washington-could-have-been-picked-as-axars-replacement-yuvraj-singh-4435076%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fchahal-or-washington-could-have-been-picked-as-axars-replacement-yuvraj-singh-4435076%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fchahal-or-washington-could-have-been-picked-as-axars-replacement-yuvraj-singh-4435076%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dianne%20Feinstein%2C%2090%2C%20Dies%3A%20Oldest%20Sitting%20Senator%20and%20Fixture%20of%20California%20Politics%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696035211000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104055231%2Cimgsize-832634.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdianne-feinstein-90-dies-oldest-sitting-senator-and-fixture-of-california-politics%2Farticleshow%2F104055213.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104055213.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdianne-feinstein-90-dies-oldest-sitting-senator-and-fixture-of-california-politics%2Farticleshow%2F104055213.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHow%20Would%20Other%20Countries%20React%20If...%26quot%3B%3A%20S%20Jaishankar%20On%20Canada%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20India%20does%20not%20require%20lessons%20from%20others%20on%20the%20concept%20of%20freedom%20of%20speech%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%2Cin%20an%20apparent%20reference%20to%20Canada%2C%20said%20that%20freedom%20of%20expression%20should%20not%20extend%20to%20incitement%20of%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Washington%20DC%20on%20Friday%2C%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B%E2%80%A6I%20flagged%20here%20(in%20US)%2C%20and%20I%20flagged%20this%20to%20the%20Canadians%20as%20well.%20We%20are%20a%20democracy.%20We%20don't%20need%20to%20learn%20from%20other%20people%20what%20freedom%20of%20speech%20is%20about%2C%20but%20we%20can%20tell%20people%20this%E2%80%A6we%20don't%20think%20freedom%20of%20speech%20extends%20to%20incitement%20to%20violence.%20That%20to%20us%2C%20is%20the%20misuse%20of%20freedom%2C%20that's%20not%20defence%20of%20freedom%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20posed%20a%20question%2C%20asking%20how%20other%20countries%20would%20react%20if%20they%20were%20in%20India's%20position%2C%20with%20their%20diplomats%2C%20embassies%2C%20and%20citizens%20facing%20intimidation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20would%20you%20react%20if%20you%20were%20in%20my%20shoes%3F%20If%20it%20was%20your%20diplomats%2C%20your%20embassy%2C%20your%20people%2C%20what%20would%20be%20your%20reaction%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20asked%20about%20Indian%20concerns%20regarding%20the%20attack%20on%20Indian%20consulate%20in%20San%20Francisco%20in%20July%20this%20year%2C%20the%20EAM%20said%20that%20the%20issue%20was%20raised%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20the%20US%20and%20described%20it%20as%20an%20ongoing%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20of%20course%20we%20raised%2C%20it.%20What%20is%20the%20status%E2%80%A6it's%20an%20ongoing%20conversation...Yes%2C%20I%20did%20spend%20some%20time%20on%20it...Yes%2C%20we%20discussed%20other%20things...Our%20relationship%20has%20many%20dimensions%2C%20many%20areas%20of%20cooperation.%20When%20we%20look%20at%20the%20world%2C%20there%20are%20areas%20we%20have%20convergences%2C%20and%20intersections%20of%20interest%20where%20we%20work%20very%20closely%20together%2C%20we%20are%20doing%20all%20of%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BLook%2C%20I%20want%20to%20be%20fair.%20If%20something%20is%20discussed%2C%20I%20am%20transparent%20about%20it.%20I%20have%20no%20problem%20saying%20yes%20we%20discussed%20it.%20I%20don't%20want%20you%20to%20think%20that%20in%20the%20India-US%20relationship%2C%20there%20is%20only%20one%20issue.%20I%20would%20say%20yes%2C%20it's%20an%20ongoing%20conversation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20July%20this%20year%2C%20a%20group%20of%20pro-Khalistan%20supporters%20allegedly%20attempted%20to%20set%20fire%20to%20the%20Consulate%20in%20San%20Francisco.%20There%20was%20no%20major%20damage%20nor%20any%20injuries%20and%20police%20were%20carrying%20out%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20US%20strongly%20condemned%20the%20reported%20vandalism%20and%20attempted%20arson%20by%20pro-Khalistan%20supporters%20against%20the%20Indian%20Consulate%20in%20San%20Francisco.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696035120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fg5mlpse8_s-jaishankar_625x300_27_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-canada-row-s-jaishankar-on-canada-row-in-us-4437068%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stating%20that%20India%20does%20not%20require%20lessons%20from%20others%20on%20the%20concept%20of%20freedom%20of%20speech%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%2Cin%20an%20apparent%20reference%20to%20Canada%2C%20said%20that%20freedom%20of%20expression%20should%20not%20extend%20to%20incitement%20of%20violence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-canada-row-s-jaishankar-on-canada-row-in-us-4437068%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-canada-row-s-jaishankar-on-canada-row-in-us-4437068%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-canada-row-s-jaishankar-on-canada-row-in-us-4437068%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Film%20Academy%20Executive%20Patrick%20Harrison%20Joins%20Frank%20PR%20to%20Launch%20Awards%20and%20Events%20Division%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696033721000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fv