nment%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20account%20posted.%20%26quot%3BLet's%20hope%20AfD%20wins%20the%20elections%20to%20stop%20this%20European%20suicide.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfD%20is%20Alternative%20for%20Germany%2C%20a%20far-right%20political%20party%20that%20campaigns%20against%20migration%20to%20Europe%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20has%20strong%20ties%20with%20right-wing%20extremists%2C%20including%20those%20of%20an%20%26quot%3Boutright%20neo-Nazi%20nature%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.spiegel.de%2Finternational%2Fgermany%2Fdangerous-liaisons-the-true-proximity-of-germany-s-afd-to-neo-nazis-a-e69c51d3-4b3c-49d2-8d54-d7b0a19c3f9a%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvestigation%20by%20Der%20Spiegel%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20party%20attracted%2022%25%20support%20in%20an%20opinion%20poll%20this%20month%2C%20compared%20to%2016%25%20for%20Chancellor%20Sholz's%20center-left%20Social%20Democrat%20Party%2C%20a%20rise%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2Fworld-politics%2F2023%2F9%2F6%2F23859900%2Fgermany-far-right-afd-comeback%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20alarmed%3C%2Fa%3E%20some%20historians%20of%20Nazi%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGermany's%20Foreign%20Office%2C%20for%20its%20part%2C%20used%20its%20verified%20X%20account%20to%20address%20Musk's%20criticism%20with%20an%20admission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20posted.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20it's%20called%20saving%20lives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EYes.%20And%20it%E2%80%99s%20called%20saving%20lives.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F7eTCbKhG8w%5C%