son%20for%20SOS%20Humanity%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConsidering%20that%20on%20average%20one%20person%20dies%20every%20three%20hours%20in%20the%20Mediterranean%20Sea%20while%20fleeing%2C%20two%20million%20euros%20for%20search%20and%20rescue%20in%20this%20year's%20federal%20budget%20is%20more%20than%20sobering%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaldenhoff%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMusk's%20turn%20toward%20right-wing%20causes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMusk's%20foray%20into%20German%20politics%20comes%20after%20a%20public%20and%20dramatic%20shift%20to%20the%20right%20for%20the%20businessman.%20After%20claiming%20to%20be%20some%20type%20of%20%26quot%3Bsocialist%26quot%3B%20in%202018%2C%20Musk%20last%20year%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-says-will-vote-republican-next-us-presidential-election-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eendorsed%20the%20Republican%20Party%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20has%20exercised%20his%20control%20over%20X%20to%20address%20right-wing%20grievances%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffree-speech-absolutist-elon-musk-censors-employees-critics-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtent%20moderation%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20promote%20claims%20from%20far-right%20influencers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20immigrant%20from%20South%20Africa%2C%20Musk%20has%20used%20his%20platform%20of%20more%20than%20158%20million%20followers%20on%20X%20to%20share%20everything%20from%20attacks%20on%20trans%20rights%20(he%20has%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-comments-relationship-transgender-daughter-vivian-jenna-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eestranged%20trans%20daughter%3C%2Fa%3E)%20to%20a%20pro-Russia%20plan%20for%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmusk-floated-ukraine-peace-plan-at-summit-before-tweeting-nyt-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epeace%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20in%20Ukraine%20(where%2