Affairs%20Minister%20trying%20to%20dodge%20the%20question%20on%20treatment%20of%20religious%20minorities%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20particularly%20unfortunate%20moment%20for%20S.%20Jaishankar%20to%20parrot%20lines%20about%20material%20%E2%80%9Cbenefits%E2%80%9D%20as%20a%20response%20to%20serious%20questions%20on%20the%20status%20of%20minorities%20in%20India.%20Just%20a%20few%20facts%20and%20analyses%20from%20this%20month%20would%20fly%20in%20the%20face%20of%20claims%20made%20by%20Jaishankar.%20India%E2%80%99s%20democratic%20backsliding%2C%20starkly%20visible%20across%20several%20global%20indices%2C%20has%20the%20diminishing%20status%20of%20minorities%20as%20a%20very%20important%20component%20of%20the%20regression.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Massive%2C%20systematic%20and%20dangerous%E2%80%99%20rights%20situation%20in%20India%3A%20UN%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20Special%20Rapporteur%20on%20Minority%20Issues%2C%20Fernand%20de%20Varennes%20speaking%20in%20Washington%20DC%20at%20an%20open%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fun-expert-says-india-risks-becoming-one-of-the-main-generators-of-instability-atrocities%5C%22%3Ehearing%20on%20September%2020%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20used%20strong%20words%20to%20characterise%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdeteriorating%E2%80%9D%20rights%20situation%20in%20India%20as%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uscirf.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FFernand%2520de%2520Varennes%2520Testimony.pdf%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cmassive%2C%20systematic%20and%20dangerous%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20opening%20remarks%20at%20a%20hearing%20on%20policy%20options%20for%20advancing%20religious%20freedom%20in%20India%2C%20organised%20by%20the%20US%20Commission%20on%20International%20Religious%20Freedom%20(USCIRF)%20in%20Washington%20DC%20on%20September%2020%2C%202023%2C%20De%20Varennes%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20risks%20becoming%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20main%20generators%20of%20instability%2C%20atrocities%20and%20violence%2C%20because%20of%20the%20massive%20scale%20and%20gravity%20of%20the%20violations%20and%20abuses%20targeting%20mainly%20religious%20and%20other%20minorities%20such%20as%20Muslims%2C%20Christians%2C%20Sikhs%20and%20others.%20It%20is%20not%20just%20individual%20or%20local%2C%20it%20is%20systematic%20and%20a%20reflection%20of%20religious%20nationalism.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvwxHnJ1P-FQ%26ab_channel%3DTheWire%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FvwxHnJ1P-FQ%3Fsi%3D8CGL6AO8rmLBwrEX%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlso%20looking%20at%20Tajikistan%2C%20Varennes%20went%20out%20and%20compared%20how%20the%20status%20there%20%E2%80%9Cpales%20in%20comparison%E2%80%9D%20if%20you%20look%20at%20India.%20He%20spoke%20of%20a%20steady%20and%20alarming%20erosion%20of%20fundamental%20rights%2C%20particularly%20for%20religious%20and%20other%20minorities%20from%20the%20review%20of%20communications%20from%202011%20to%20now%3A%20By%202022%2C%20almost%20all%20of%20them%20involve%20grave%20allegations%20of%20denial%20of%20fundamental%20rights%2C%20particularly%20targeting%20religious%20minorities.%C2%A0From%20May%2012%2C%202020%20to%20May%2023%2C%202023%2C%20%5Bthey%20issued%5D%20around%2046%20communications%20and%20an%20estimated%2020%20press%20releases.%E2%80%9D%20He%20cited%20a%20study%20that%20%E2%80%9Cnoted%20a%20786%25%20increase%20in%20hate%20crimes%20against%20minorities%20between%202014%20and%202018%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EManipur%3A%20254%20churches%20destroyed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20of%20Manipur%20has%20been%20witness%2C%20as%20per%20the%20state%20police%20itself%2C%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-death-toll-violence-missing-arms%5C%22%3Edestruction%20of%20254%20churches%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20uncontrollable%20violence%20rocking%20the%20state%20since%20May%203.%20At%20least%20180%20persons%20are%20dead.%20There%20was%20a%20viral%20video%20of%20a%20mob%20chasing%20after%20three%20Kuki-Zo%20women%2C%20after%20having%20disrobed%20them.%20Police%20FIRs%20spoke%20of%20sexual%20violence.%20Just%20today%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court-appointed%20committee%20formed%20to%20look%20into%20the%20humanitarian%20aspects%20of%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20asked%20the%20government%20in%20the%20state%20to%20%E2%80%9Cimmediately%20identify%E2%80%9D%20all%20religious%20buildings%20in%20the%20state%20and%20protect%20them%20from%20damage%20and%20encroachment.%20The%20government%20itself%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Funion-govt-terming-manipur-tensions-communal-violence-for-compensation-disbursal-report%5C%22%3Etermed%20the%20violence%20as%20%E2%80%9Ccommunal%20violence%E2%80%9D%2C%20according%20to%20reports.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAttacks%20on%20Christians%20up%20by%20four%20times%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBetween%202011%20and%202022%2C%20attacks%20against%20Christians%20went%20up%20by%20four%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflo.uri.sh%2Fvisualisation%2F14958889%2Fembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Interactive%20or%20visual%20content%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EData%20put%20out%20by%20the%20United%20Christian%20Forum%20(UCF)%20%E2%80%93%20a%20civil%20society%20organisation%20focused%20on%20Christian%20issues%20%E2%80%93%20released%20a%20stunning%20statistic%20on%20September%207%3A%20there%20have%20been%20525%20attacks%20against%20Christians%20in%20India%20just%20in%20the%20first%20eight%20months%20of%202023.%20If%20this%20trend%20were%20to%20continue%2C%20this%20would%20prove%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20most%20violent%20and%20difficult%20years%20the%20Christian%20community%20in%20India%20has%20ever%20seen%2C%20breaking%20the%20recent%20record%20set%20by%202022%2C%20and%202021%20before%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20leader%20abuses%20Muslim%20MP%20in%20parliament%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBJP%20MP%20from%20South%20Delhi%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSvJGsiizlbo%26ab_channel%3DTheWire%5C%22%3ERamesh%20Bidhuri%20in%20the%20new%20building%20for%20Parliament%2C%20hurled%20Islamophobic%20slurs%20and%20abuses%20at%20Muslim%20MP%20Danish%20Ali%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20BSP%2C%20specifically%20targeting%20him%20for%20his%20identity%20as%20a%20Muslim%2C%20calling%20him%20%E2%80%98pimp%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98terrorist%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98militant%E2%80%99%20and%20also%20used%20the%20words%C2%A0%3Cem%3Emullah%3C%2Fem%3Eand%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ekatwa%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20a%20pejorative%20word%20for%20a%20Muslim%20who%20is%20circumcised%20to%20imply%20that%20he%20has%20been%20castrated.%20Two%20former%20ministers%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20cabinet%2C%20Ravi%20Shankar%20Prasad%20and%20Harshvardhan%20can%20be%20seen%20laughing%20behind%20him.%20After%20the%20outburst%2C%20Bidhuri%20has%20not%20been%20officially%20as%20much%20as%20reprimanded%20by%20his%20party%2C%20instead%20has%20been%20promoted%20to%20a%20crucial%20position%20of%20holding%20charge%20of%20Tonk%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20seen%20as%20a%20Muslim-dominant%20area%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Hate%20and%20indoctrination%20embedded%20in%20BJP%20campaign%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20a%20series%20of%20stories%20about%20hate%20and%20indoctrination%20being%20embedded%20in%20the%20electoral%20campaign%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20just%20yesterday%20has%20detailed%20how%20BJP%20staffers%2C%20consultants%20and%20supporters%20created%20%E2%80%9Cincendiary%20posts%20designed%20to%20go%20viral%20on%20WhatsApp%E2%80%9D%20during%20the%20campaign%20for%20the%20Karnataka%20assembly%20elections.%20These%20posts%20often%20claimed%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9CMuslim%20minority%2C%20abetted%20by%20the%20secular%20and%20liberal%20Congress%20party%2C%20abused%20and%20murdered%20members%20of%20the%20Hindu%20majority%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20%E2%80%9Cjustice%20and%20security%20could%20be%20secured%20only%20through%20a%20vote%20for%20the%20BJP%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20says%20it%20was%20granted%20%E2%80%9Crare%20access%20to%20the%20%5BBJP%E2%80%99s%5D%20vast%20messaging%20machinery%20and%20the%20activists%20who%20run%20it%E2%80%9D%20during%20the%20election%20campaign%20in%20the%20southern%20state%2C%20which%20revealed%20how%20BJP%20staffers%20and%20allies%20%E2%80%9Cconceive%20and%20craft%20posts%20aimed%20at%20exploiting%20the%20fears%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Hindu%20majority%2C%20and%20detailed%20how%20they%20had%20assembled%20a%20sprawling%20apparatus%20of%20150%2C000%20social%20media%20workers%20to%20propagate%20this%20content%20across%20a%20vast%20network%20of%20WhatsApp%20groups%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Country%20of%20particular%20concern%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20Commission%20on%20International%20Religious%20Freedom%20(USCIRF)%2C%20an%20independent%2C%20bipartisan%20U.S.%20federal%20government%20agency%20created%20by%20the%201998%20International%20Religious%20Freedom%20Act.%20USCIRF%20monitors%20the%20universal%20right%20to%20freedom%20of%20religion%20or%20belief%20abroad%3B%20makes%20policy%20recommendations%20to%20the%20US%20government%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uscirf.gov%2Fnews-room%2Freleases-statements%2Fuscirf-urges-president-biden-raise-religious-freedom-concerns-during%5C%22%3Eurged%20US%20President%20Jo%20Biden%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9Cto%20address%20concerning%20issues%20of%20religious%20freedom%20and%20other%20related%20human%20rights%20in%20India%20during%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20upcoming%20state%20visit.%20For%20the%20past%20several%20years%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20led%20by%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20has%20supported%20discriminatory%20national%20and%20state-level%20policies%20that%20severely%20hinder%20and%20restrict%20the%20religious%20freedom%20of%20minority%20groups%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said%20in%20June%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUSCIRF%20has%20recommended%20the%20U.S.%20Department%20of%20State%20designate%20India%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccountry%20of%20particular%20concern%2C%E2%80%9D%20or%20CPC%2C%20each%20year%20since%202020%2C%20for%20engaging%20in%20systematic%2C%20ongoing%2C%20and%20egregious%20violations%20of%20religious%20freedom%2C%20and%20again%20most%20recently%20in%20its%202023%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uscirf.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2023-05%2FIndia%25202023.pdf%5C%22%3EAnnual%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E.%20USCIRF%20also%20published%20an%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uscirf.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2023%2520India%2520Apostasy%2520Issue%2520Update.pdf%5C%22%3Eissue%20update%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20India%E2%80%99s%20state-level%20anti-conversion%20laws%2C%20providing%20further%20context%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20use%20of%20these%20laws%20to%20target%20religious%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Ffree_thinker%2Fstatus%2F1707775528839545297%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3EAs%20Pratik%20Sinha%2C%20founder%20of%20%3Cem%3EAlt%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20noted%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20templated%20answer%20that%20BJP%20has%20chosen%20to%20respond%20to%20all%20questions%20concerning%20minorities%20%E2%80%93%20that%20social%20welfare%20is%20extended%20to%20everyone.%20The%20whole%20party%20apparatus%20of%20BJP%2C%20from%20top%20to%20bottom%2C%20is%20involved%20in%20dehumanising%20Muslims%20in%20Indi