sit%20at%206.9%20per%20cent%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Fgovt-hikes-interest-rate-to-6-7-on-five-year-recurring-deposit-scheme-123092900898_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Fgovt-hikes-interest-rate-to-6-7-on-five-year-recurring-deposit-scheme-123092900898_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Fgovt-hikes-interest-rate-to-6-7-on-five-year-recurring-deposit-scheme-123092900898_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20a%20Book%20of%20Urdu%20Poetry%20Came%20to%20be%20Printed%20in%20Kutch%20in%201860%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F29165247%2FOld-book.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%201860%2C%20a%20book%20of%20Urdu%20poetry%20was%20published%20by%20a%20printing%20press%20at%20Bhuj%2C%20the%20capital%20of%20the%20kingdom%20of%20Kutch.%20At%20a%20time%20when%20most%20princely%20states%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Maharashtra%20did%20not%20have%20a%20printing%20press%2C%20how%20did%20print%20reach%20the%20remotest%20corner%20of%20western%20India%3F%20And%20why%20was%20the%20book%20printed%20in%20Urdu%2C%20a%20modern%20Indian%20language%20with%20no%20ostensible%20local%20connections%20in%20Kutch%3F%20And%20why%20did%20it%20mostly%20contain%20verses%20in%20praise%20of%20officials%20of%20the%20East%20India%20Company%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20know%20where%20Baboo%20Saheb%20is%20right%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20complained%20Ghalib%20in%20a%20letter%20written%20on%20June%205%2C%201853%20to%20his%20Agra-based%20friend%2C%20Munshi%20Hargopal.%20%E2%80%9CIs%20he%20up%20in%20the%20hills%20of%20Mount%20Abu%20or%20has%20he%20come%20to%20Bharatpur%3F%20There%20is%20no%20reason%20why%20he%20may%20have%20gone%20to%20Ajmer.%20After%20enduring%20what%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20never-ending%20wait%2C%20I%20now%20write%20to%20you.%20In%20your%20reply%20to%20this%20letter%2C%20you%20should%20let%20me%20know%20what%20you%20think%20could%20be%20the%20reason%20for%20the%20delay%20in%20his%20response.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJani%20Behari%20Lall%2C%20alias%20Baboo%20Saheb%2C%20was%20a%20man%20on%20the%20move%20in%20the%201850s.%20And%20the%20arena%20of%20his%20peregrinations%20was%20Rajputana%2C%20a%20sprawling%20territory%20fractured%20into%2016%20princely%20states%2C%20big%20and%20small%2C%20all%20under%20the%20overlordship%20of%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20East%20India%20Company%20through%20its%20Rajputana%20Agency%2C%20instituted%20in%201832.%20The%20Agent%20to%20the%20Governor-General%2C%20generally%20a%20military%20officer%2C%20was%20the%20paramount%20authority.%20He%20was%20based%20in%20Ajmer%20but%20summered%20in%20the%20pleasanter%20climes%20of%20Mount%20Abu.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMunshi%20Hargopal%20had%20introduced%20Jani%20Behari%20Lall%20to%20Ghalib%20earlier%20in%20the%20year%20in%20Delhi.%20Though%20Jani%20was%20already%20a%20prolific%20poet%2C%20he%20immediately%20adopted%20Ghalib%20as%20his%20ustad%20in%20Urdu%20poetry%20by%20offering%20a%20%3Cem%3Enazrana%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eof%20a%20hundred%20rupees.%20As%20a%20further%20favour%2C%20he%20presented%20the%20royal%20court%20of%20Jaipur%2C%20where%20the%20ruler%20Sawai%20Ram%20Singh%20(1833%E2%80%931880)%20had%20just%20attained%20adulthood%2C%20with%20a%20compilation%20of%20Ghalib%E2%80%99s%20verses.%20This%20was%20in%20the%20hope%20that%20Ghalib%20would%20be%20granted%20a%20cash%20award%20or%20a%20monthly%20allowance.%20And%20Ghalib%20was%20now%20keen%20to%20hear%20the%20outcome%20of%20Jani%E2%80%99s%20efforts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGhalib%20had%20had%20numerous%20disappointing%20encounters%20with%20the%20rich%20and%20powerful%20and%20was%20not%20very%20hopeful%20of%20success.%20His%20panegyrics%20had%20either%20been%20ignored%20by%20the%20royal%20addressees%20or%20he%20had%20been%20choused%20out%20of%20the%20monetary%20awards%20by%20unscrupulous%20intermediaries.%20Jani%20Behari%20Lall%20was%2C%20however%2C%20not%20cast%20in%20that%20mould.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20310px)%2085vw%2C%20310px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F29170039%2FImage-2.-Jani-Behari-Lall-233x300.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22310%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F29170039%2FImage-2.-Jani-Behari-Lall-233x300.jpg%20233w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F29170039%2FImage-2.-Jani-Behari-Lall.jpg%20727w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-677544%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EJani%20Behari%20Lall%20alias%20Baboo%20Saheb%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20Photo%20provided%20by%20author.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESteeped%20in%20the%20courtly%20practices%20of%20Rajputana%2C%20Jani%20Behari%20Lall%20hailed%20from%20a%20family%20of%20bureaucrats%20who%20were%20settled%20in%20Bharatpur%20for%20a%20few%20generations.%20They%20were%20Gujarati%20Nagar%20Brahmins%2C%20a%20community%20whose%20members%20traditionally%20occupied%20the%20highest%20administrative%20posts%20in%20the%20princely%20courts%20of%20Rajputana%20and%20Saurashtra.%20For%20example%2C%20during%20the%20long%20twilight%20of%20the%20Mughal%20empire%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20Raja%20Chhabilaram%20(1665-1719)%20and%20his%20family%20wielded%20great%20influence%20on%20its%20political%20affairs.%20In%20the%20early%20nineteenth%20century%2C%20Ranchhodjee%20Amarjee%20(1768-1841)%2C%20succeeded%20his%20father%20and%20brother%20as%20the%20dewan%20of%20Junagadh.%20Both%20of%20them%20were%20scholars%20whose%20Persian%20correspondence%20was%20compiled%20to%20serve%20as%20epistolary%20exemplars.%20Ranchhodjee%2C%20besides%20other%20works%2C%20also%20wrote%20a%20Persian%20history%20of%20western%20Saurashtra%20titled%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Tarikh-i-Sorath%20va%20Halar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20domination%20of%20the%20Nagar%20Brahmin%20community%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20whose%20number%20would%20never%20have%20exceeded%20a%20hundred%20thousand%2C%20in%20the%20higher%20echelons%20of%20bureaucracy%2C%20as%20well%20as%20other%20fields%20such%20as%20literature%20and%20academics%2C%20continued%20well%20into%20the%2020th%20century.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMembers%20of%20the%20Jani%20clan%20(the%20name%20is%20a%20corruption%20of%20Yagnik%2C%20a%20category%20of%20priests)%20had%20occupied%20positions%20in%20the%20administrative%20hierarchy%20in%20the%20kingdom%20of%20Bharatpur%20for%20generations.%20Often%2C%20these%20positions%20were%20hereditary%2C%20but%20aspirants%20still%20needed%20to%20acquire%20the%20necessary%20expertise.%20In%20early%201853%2C%20when%20Ghalib%20was%20waiting%20to%20hear%20from%20him%2C%20Jani%20Behari%20Lall%20was%20the%20naib-vakeel%20or%20deputy%20emissary%20of%20Bharatpur%20to%20the%20Agent%20to%20the%20Governor-General%20in%20Rajputana.%20But%20he%20had%20not%20taken%20the%20traditional%20route%20to%20get%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBorn%20around%20the%20year%201810%2C%20Jani%20studied%20at%20the%20English%20school%20in%20Agra%2C%20a%20mere%20fifty%20miles%20to%20the%20east%20of%20Bharatpur.%20Jani%20was%20among%20the%20first%20generation%20of%20north%20Indians%20to%20receive%20a%20formal%20education%20in%20English.%20He%20later%20moved%20to%20Benares%20where%20he%20studied%20at%20the%20Sanskrit%20College.%20By%20the%20time%20he%20completed%20his%20education%2C%20Jani%2C%20like%20many%20other%20educated%20young%20men%20of%20that%20time%2C%20was%20well-versed%20in%20Sanskrit%2C%20Persian%2C%20Arabic%20and%20English.%20But%20he%20developed%20a%20special%20affinity%20for%20a%20language%20which%20had%20coalesced%20into%20definitive%20shape%20only%20in%20the%20late%20eighteenth%20century%3A%20Urdu.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20details%20of%20Jani%20Behari%20Lall%E2%80%99s%20early%20career%20are%20hazy%20and%20conflicting.%20He%20may%20have%20started%20his%20career%20as%20a%20teacher%20in%20the%201830s%20at%20the%20school%20established%20by%20Baboo%20Fateh%20Narain%2C%20a%20scion%20of%20the%20ruling%20house%20of%20Benares.%20In%201843%2C%20he%20was%20teaching%20at%20the%20Victoria%20College%2C%20Benares.%20When%20a%20newly%20appointed%20principal%20attempted%20to%20restructure%20the%20educational%20system%20in%20Benares%20and%20unify%20the%20Sanskrit%20and%20English%20sections%2C%20Jani%20was%20among%20the%20teachers%20who%20were%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20these%20reforms.%20Eventually%2C%20Jani%20decided%20to%20explore%20other%20career%20options.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20mid-1840s%2C%20Jani%20Behari%20Lall%20joined%20the%20sixty-second%20regiment%20of%20the%20Bengal%20Native%20Infantry.%20He%20was%20the%20regimental%20schoolmaster.%20Jani%20travelled%20to%20many%20places%20in%20Bengal%20with%20his%20regiment%20going%20as%20far%20east%20as%20Dhaka.%20This%20was%20the%20period%20when%20the%20East%20India%20Company%20vigorously%20followed%20a%20policy%20of%20expansion%20through%20wars%20and%20conquered%20Punjab%20and%20a%20large%20part%20of%20Burma.%20The%20Doctrine%20of%20Lapse%20was%20also%20used%20to%20annex%20Indian%20royal%20states.%20Its%20army%20was%20always%20on%20standby%2C%20ready%20to%20march%20at%20short%20notice.%20Jani%20must%20have%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20observe%20these%20political%20machinations%20at%20close%20quarters%20for%20the%20eight%20years%20that%20he%20was%20with%20the%20Native%20Infantry.%20This%20stint%20also%20gave%20him%20the%20opportunity%20to%20develop%20relationships%20with%20European%20officials%20in%20the%20military%20and%20administrative%20cadres.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20his%20elder%20brother%2C%20Jani%20Bankey%20Lall%2C%20who%20was%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Evakeel%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20the%20state%20of%20Bharatpur%20at%20the%20Rajputana%20Agency%2C%20died%20in%20the%20early%201850s%2C%20Jani%20Behari%20Lall%20was%20requisitioned%20by%20the%20Bharatpur%20Maharaja%20to%20act%20in%20his%20stead%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Enaib-vakeel%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20After%20the%20ruler%2C%20Balwant%20Singh%2C%20died%20in%201853%20leaving%20behind%20an%20infant%20son%2C%20Bharatpur%20entered%20a%20period%20of%20uncertainty.%20Jani%20Behari%20Lall%20might%20have%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20ensuring%20a%20successful%20transition%20until%20Jaswant%20Singh%20(1851%E2%80%931893)%20was%20placed%20on%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Egaddi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%201854%2C%20Jani%20Behari%20Lall%20had%20a%20new%20role%20in%20the%20same%20setting.%20Instead%20of%20being%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Evakeel%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20an%20Indian%20state%2C%20he%20was%20now%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emunshi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20or%20secretary%20at%20the%20Rajputana%20Agency.%20Working%20closely%20with%20the%20Agent%2C%20he%20might%20have%20managed%20diplomatic%20correspondence%20with%20its%20sixteen%20ward%20states.%20This%20role%20required%20a%20command%20over%20both%20Persian%20and%20English%2C%20besides%20local%20languages.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20May%201857%2C%20most%20regiments%20of%20the%20Bengal%20Native%20Infantry%2C%20including%20the%20sixty-second%20in%20which%20Jani%20had%20served%2C%20mutinied.%20It%20was%20a%20turbulent%20period%20for%20the%20East%20India%20Company%20as%20its%20officers%20tried%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20mutiny%20did%20not%20spread%20to%20Rajputana.%20Though%20they%20could%20not%20thwart%20it%2C%20they%20were%2C%20through%20a%20combination%20of%20fortuitous%20circumstances%2C%20able%20to%20quell%20it%20at%20short%20notice.%20Unlike%20the%20ruling%20nobility%20in%20the%20environs%20of%20Delhi%2C%20none%20of%20the%20Rajput%20states%2C%20especially%20Bharatpur%2C%20supported%20the%20mutineers%20and%20this%20proved%20to%20be%20the%20decisive%20factor.%20The%20rebellion%20in%20the%20kingdom%20of%20Kutch%2C%20adjoining%20Rajputana%2C%20was%20also%20subjugated%20in%20a%20similar%20manner.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20East%20India%20Company%2C%20as%20part%20of%20its%20policy%20to%20exert%20better%20control%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20rebellion%2C%20decided%20to%20depute%20Indians%20who%20had%20worked%20in%20its%20establishment%20to%20oversee%20the%20administration%20of%20its%20client%20states.%20And%20so%20it%20was%20that%20Jani%20Behari%20Lall%20found%20himself%20designated%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edewan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20or%20chief%20minister%20of%20Kutch%20in%201858.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESandwiched%20between%20the%20two%20large%20provinces%20of%20Sindh%20and%20Gujarat%20and%20bounded%20by%20inhospitable%20salt-caked%20deserts%2C%20Kutch%20might%20seem%20a%20place%20where%20nothing%20significant%20transpired.%20But%20that%20was%20far%20from%20the%20reality.%20Kutch%20had%20its%20fair%20share%20of%20action%3A%20border%20skirmishes%2C%20assassinations%2C%20fratricides%2C%20and%2C%20once%2C%20in%201741%2C%20a%20Kutchi%20prince%20named%20Lakhpat%2C%20emulating%20the%20Mughal%20emperor%20Aurangzeb%2C%20usurped%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20kingdom%20and%20imprisoned%20him%20until%20he%20died.%20Its%20long%20coastline%20facilitated%20a%20thriving%20maritime%20economy%20and%20Kutchi%20ships%20called%20at%20Indian%20Ocean%20ports%20from%20Zanzibar%20and%20Muscat%20in%20the%20west%20to%20Sumatra%20and%20Java%20in%20the%20east.%20Besides%20a%20brisk%20trade%20in%20salt%20and%20agricultural%20produce%2C%20Kutch%20was%20the%20entrep%C3%B4t%20for%20African%20slaves%20and%20Malwa%20opium.%20Its%20importance%20in%2018th%20century%20trade%20networks%20of%20western%20India%20can%20be%20gauged%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20Tipu%20Sultan%20of%20Mysore%20had%20established%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfactory%E2%80%9D%20in%20Bhuj%20to%20further%20his%20international%20trading%20interests.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F29165845%2F1878-map-of-Kutch.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22805%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F29165845%2F1878-map-of-Kutch.jpg%20805w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F29165845%2F1878-map-of-Kutch-300x206.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-677543%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22553%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAn%201878%20map%20of%20Kutch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20Tipu%20Sultan%E2%80%99s%20death%20in%201799%2C%20this%20investment%20provided%20the%20East%20India%20Company%20with%20an%20excuse%20to%20establish%20direct%20contact%20with%20the%20kingdom%20of%20Kutch%20as%20they%20sought%20to%20claim%20his%20assets.%20They%20soon%20deputed%20a%20Political%20Resident%20to%20Kutch%2C%20and%20within%20two%20decades%2C%20in%201819%2C%20manoeuvred%20to%20depose%20the%20reigning%20king.%20His%20five-year-old%20son%20was%20installed%20on%20the%20throne%20with%20the%20titular%20name%20of%20Maharao%20Deshalji%20II.%20When%20Jani%20arrived%20in%20Bhuj%20in%201858%2C%20Deshalji%2C%20now%20in%20his%20forties%20and%20unwell%2C%20still%20occupied%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Egaddi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJani%20Behari%20Lall%2C%20as%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edewan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20who%20had%20been%20imposed%20on%20the%20state%2C%20might%20have%20faced%20a%20hostile%20reception%20from%20the%20numerous%20power%20centres%20in%20the%20Kutchi%20court.%20But%20by%20deftly%20defusing%20a%20succession%20crisis%20which%20had%20been%20precipitated%20by%20Deshalji%20who%20wanted%20his%20younger%20son%20to%20succeed%20him%20rather%20than%20the%20crown%20prince%2C%20Jani%20seems%20to%20have%20established%20his%20clout.%20As%20a%20means%20of%20exercising%20effective%20administrative%20control%2C%20Jani%20compiled%20and%20codified%20all%20the%20extant%20local%20laws.%20And%20perhaps%2C%20it%20was%20to%20print%20this%20Kutchi%20law%20code%20that%20Jani%20Behari%20Lall%20requisitioned%20a%20printing%20press.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHaving%20spent%20his%20youth%20in%20Agra%2C%20Jani%20Behari%20Lall%20would%20have%20been%20very%20familiar%20with%20the%20printing%20press%20and%20its%20products.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAgra%20Akhbar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20first%20Urdu%20newspaper%20from%20the%20city%2C%20began%20its%20career%20in%201831.%20Agra%E2%80%99s%20first%20Persian%20weekly%20newspaper%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EZubdatul%20Akhbar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20came%20into%20existence%20in%201833%20and%20was%20long-lived.%20The%20Agra%20Mission%20Press%20and%20the%20Secundra%20Orphanage%20Press%2C%20both%20established%20in%20the%20late%20thirties%2C%20printed%20prolifically%20in%20many%20languages.%20By%20the%201850s%2C%20the%20cities%20of%20Lucknow%2C%20Delhi%20and%20Allahabad%20had%20also%20emerged%20as%20major%20print%20centres.%20One%20can%20imagine%20Jani%20as%20a%20diligent%20peruser%20of%20newspapers%20and%20a%20buyer%20of%20printed%20books%20in%20Urdu%20and%20Persian.%20One%20of%20his%20verses%20goes%20thus%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20in%20love%20with%20books%2C%20say%20Raazi%3B%20because%20a%20book%20is%20a%20man%E2%80%99s%20best%20friend.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20printing%20press%20at%20Bhuj%20was%20known%20as%20the%20Kutch%20Durbar%20Press.%20It%20was%20the%20first%20to%20be%20established%20in%20a%20princely%20state%20of%20Rajputana%20or%20Saurashtra.%20No%20further%20details%20are%20forthcoming%20about%20the%20press%20which%20Jani%20set%20up%20but%20it%20seems%20to%20have%20become%20operational%20in%201859.%20The%20lithographic%20press%2C%20could%20have%20been%20sourced%20from%20either%20Bombay%20or%20Ahmedabad%20and%20a%20trained%20printer%20might%20have%20accompanied%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20from%20the%20Kutch%20Durbar%20Press%20that%20the%20aforementioned%20Urdu%20book%20was%20published%20in%20Hijri%201277%20(October%201860).%20And%20it%20was%20a%20book%20of%20poetry%20composed%20by%20Jani%20Behari%20Lall%20who%20wrote%20Urdu%20verse%20under%20the%20pen%20name%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3Etakhallus%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20%E2%80%98Raazi%E2%80%99.%20Titled%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMuntakhab%20Qasaid%20va%20Ghazaliyat%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%5BSelected%20Qasidas%20and%20Ghazals%5D%2C%20the%20book%20runs%20175%20pages.%20Lithographed%20on%20cream-coloured%20locally%20made%20paper%2C%20the%20text%20is%20neatly%20laid%20out%20in%20two%20columns%20with%20generous%20margins.%20The%20scribe%20who%20copied%20the%20lithographed%20text%20was%20Miyanji%20Abdulla%20bin%20Miyanji%20Ibrahim%2C%20a%20native%20of%20Mandvi%2C%20the%20largest%20port%20in%20Kutch.%20Abdulla%20wrote%20in%20a%20steady%20but%20slightly%20cramped%20style.%20The%20floral%20embellishments%20are%2C%20however%2C%20ineptly%20done.%20The%20print%20quality%20of%20the%20book%20is%20mediocre%20as%20might%20be%20expected%20in%20a%20newly%20set%20up%20lithographic%20press%2C%20perhaps%20operated%20by%20an%20inexperienced%20lithographer.%20The%20inking%20is%20uneven%20in%20most%20pages%20rendering%20the%20text%20illegible%20at%20places.%20The%20text%20does%20not%20contain%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edibacha%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(foreword)%20or%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Etaqriz%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(laudatory%20blurbs)%2C%20standard%20features%20of%20contemporary%20Urdu%20poetry%20books.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20first%20third%20of%20the%20book%20comprises%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eqasidas%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eor%20laudatory%20poems.%20The%20recipients%20of%20praise%20from%20Jani%E2%80%99s%20pen%20are%20mostly%20European%20military%20officials%20ranging%20from%20lowly%20lieutenants%20to%20colonels%20commanding%20his%20regiment.%20Jani%20would%20have%20worked%20with%20them%20during%20his%20stint%20in%20the%20Bengal%20Native%20Infantry.%20He%20also%20includes%20an%20application%20for%20redress%2C%20written%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20long%20poem%2C%20addressed%20to%20the%20principal%20of%20Benares%20College%20in%201844.%20His%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eghazals%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20account%20for%20more%20than%20half%20the%20book%2C%20were%20judged%20as%20competent%20by%20his%20contemporaries%2C%20even%20if%20he%20verged%20on%20prurience%20occasionally.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20highlight%20of%20the%20book%20is%20a%20biography%20of%20Jani%20Behari%20Lall%20himself%2C%20composed%20in%20Persian%20verse%20by%20a%20Kutchi%20poet%20named%20Munshi%20Amin%20Ahmed%20Sahba.%20Though%20it%20is%20composed%20in%20the%20highfalutin%E2%80%99%20style%20characteristic%20of%20such%20encomiums%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eqasida%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20traces%20Jani%E2%80%99s%20career%20from%20his%20early%20days%20in%20Agra%20and%20Benares%20to%20his%20exploits%20in%20the%20Rajputana%20Agency%20at%20Ajmer%20and%20Mount%20Abu%20before%20he%20arrived%20in%20Kutch.%20He%20then%20mentions%20the%20high%20regard%20with%20which%20he%20was%20held%20by%20senior%20officials%20of%20the%20East%20India%20Company.%20At%20Kutch%2C%20he%20credits%20Jani%20with%20establishing%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%20Some%20of%20the%20biographical%20details%20in%20this%20article%20account%20are%20based%20on%20this%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eqasida%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20prominent%20Urdu%20poet%2C%20Jani%20Behari%20Lall%20features%20in%20many%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Etazkiras%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(biographical%20dictionaries%20of%20poets)%2C%20but%20their%20authors%2C%20such%20as%20Lala%20Sri%20Ram%20who%20wrote%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKhumkhana-e%20Javed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20do%20not%20seem%20to%20have%20seen%20this%20book.%20Nor%20has%20Malik%20Ram%2C%20who%20profiled%20Jani%20in%20his%20account%20of%20Ghalib%E2%80%99s%20contemporaries%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETalamiza-e%20Ghalib%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20death%20of%20Maharao%20Deshalji%20in%201860%2C%20Jani%20Behari%20Lall%20could%20not%20long%20survive%20the%20change%20in%20regime%20at%20Kutch.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20returned%20to%20Bharatpur%20in%201861%20where%20he%20enjoyed%20a%20long%20tenure%20as%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Evakeel%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20In%20the%20mid-1870s%2C%20he%20was%20appointed%20guardian%20of%20a%20teenage%20Sajjan%20Singh%2C%20who%20had%20just%20become%20the%20ruler%20of%20Mewar.%20He%20seems%20to%20have%20been%20associated%20with%20the%20Bharatpur%20court%20even%20in%20the%201890s%20and%20was%20in%20receipt%20of%20a%20pension%20until%20his%20death%20in%201897.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20188px)%2085vw%2C%20188px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F29171025%2FMirza-Ghalib-188x300.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22188%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F29171025%2FMirza-Ghalib-188x300.jpg%20188w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F29171025%2FMirza-Ghalib.jpg%20290w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-677548%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMirza%20Ghalib.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons.%20Public%20domain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhether%20the%20relationship%20between%20Mirza%20Ghalib%20and%20Jani%20Behari%20Lall%20endured%20after%201853%20is%20not%20known%2C%20but%20Ghalib%20did%20get%20a%20cash%20award%20of%20three%20hundred%20rupees%20from%20the%20Jaipur%20court%20thanks%20to%20Jani%E2%80%99s%20intercession.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJani%20continued%20his%20literary%20activities%20and%20published%20numerous%20books%2C%20most%20of%20them%20printed%20at%20the%20Matba%20Mufeed-e-Aam%2C%20an%20Agra%20printery%20which%20also%20published%20a%20few%20of%20Ghalib%E2%80%99s%20works.%20His%20works%2C%20available%20in%20a%20few%20libraries%2C%20include%20a%20grammar%20of%20the%20Arabic%20language%2C%20a%20handbook%20of%20the%20Persian%20and%20English%20languages%2C%20and%20Urdu%20translations%20of%20Persian%20classical%20texts%20such%20as%20Gulistan%2C%20Bostan%20and%20Anwar-i%20Suhayli.%20He%20is%20also%20known%20to%20have%20written%20an%20autobiography%20which%20is%20lost.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENot%20much%20has%20survived%20of%20Jani%E2%80%99s%20legacy%2C%20including%20his%20papers%20and%20correspondence.%20A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edharamshala%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20built%20in%20Samvat%201941%20(1884%2F85)%20by%20Jani%20Behari%20Lall%20and%20his%20nephew%20Jani%20Ganapati%20Lall%20in%20memory%20of%20Jani%20Bankey%20Lall%20is%20all%20that%20survives%20in%20Bharatpur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Kutch%20Durbar%20Press%20established%20by%20Jani%20Behari%20Lall%20was%20the%20sole%20printing%20press%20in%20all%20of%20Kutch%20for%20the%20next%20ninety%20years.%20The%20Kutchi%20court%20clamped%20down%20on%20printing%20activities%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20even%20newspapers%20printed%20elsewhere%20could%20not%20be%20imported%20into%20the%20kingdom.%20It%20was%20only%20after%20Indian%20independence%20that%20private%20printing%20presses%20could%20be%20established%20in%20Kutch.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fmurali-ranganathan%5C%22%3EMurali%20Ranganathan%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20writer%20and%20historian%20researching%20the%2019th%20century%20with%20a%20special%20focus%20on%20print%20history%20and%20culture.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695989455000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F29165247%2FOld-book.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fhow-a-book-of-urdu-poetry-came-to-be-published-in-remote-kutch-in-1860%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20was%20a%20period%20when%20most%20princely%20states%20in%20Gujarat%20and%20western%20India%20did%20not%20have%20printing%20presses.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fhow-a-book-of-urdu-poetry-came-to-be-published-in-remote-kutch-in-1860%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20gives%20assent%20to%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22publ