0support%20an%20unbroken%20cold%20chain.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20only%20there%20was%20a%20way%20to%20ensure%20optimal%20temperatures%20during%20the%20last-mile%20delivery%2C%20he%20thought.%20Once%20again%20the%20ATL%20Lab%20at%20school%20was%20occupied%20for%20hours%20in%20the%20months%20to%20come.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20that%20Aditya%20produced%20this%20time%20was%20a%20thermoelectric%20device%20that%20offered%20controlled%20refrigeration.%20Called%20VacciVan%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Cnovel%20low-cost%20vaccine%20transportation%20and%20storage%20system%E2%80%9D%20is%20powered%20via%20bicycle%20pedalling.%20This%20eliminates%20the%20need%20for%20ice%20packs%20or%20external%20electricity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAditya%20elaborates%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327322%2Fretired-brigadier-p-ganesham-mentors-padma-president-award-winning-innovations-in-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20mechanism%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20bicycle%20is%20pedalled%2C%20current%20is%20generated%20through%20electromagnetism.%20The%20current%20is%20then%20stored%20and%20used%20to%20freeze%20the%20vaccines%20at%20the%20designated%202-8%20degrees%20Celsius.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECalling%20the%20innovation%20%E2%80%9Ca%20remarkable%20solution%20to%20a%20critical%20issue%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20headmistress%20at%20Aditya%E2%80%99s%20school%2C%20Vinita%20Kapoor%2C%20applauds%20him%20for%20his%20ingenuity.%20%E2%80%9CVacciVan%E2%80%99s%20versatility%20can%20benefit%20not%20only%20healthcare%20but%20also%20food%20security%20in%20low-income%20or%20remote%20areas%20with%20unstable%20electricity%20supplies%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes%20while%20talking%20about%20its%20potential%20once%20it%20is%20scaled.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22h