ote%20the%20concept%20of%20family%20forestry%20and%20letting%20trees%20thrive.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EBheraram%20says%20that%20he%20conducts%20plantation%20drives%20only%20when%20they%20are%20assured%20of%20active%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F312765%2Fhow-to-start-plantation-drive-in-my-city-kolkata-engineer-shares-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommunity%20participation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CSometimes%2C%20people%20lose%20interest%20even%20after%20taking%20the%20pledge.%20It%20is%20a%20waste%20of%20our%20efforts%20and%20resources%20if%20these%20saplings%20do%20not%20survive.%20So%2C%20we%20monitor%20the%20progress%20by%20conducting%20regular%20offline%20meetings%20as%20well%20as%20Zoom%20calls.%20We%20maintain%20records%20of%20our%20plantation%20drives%20at%20the%20village%2C%20block%2C%20district%2C%20and%20state%20levels%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%98tree%20teacher%E2%80%99%20says%20that%20the%20survival%20rate%20of%20their%20saplings%20is%20up%20to%2090%20percent.%20He%20plants%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F165796%2Frajasthan-jodhpur-bishnoi-trees-environment-india-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enative%20trees%20%3C%2Fa%3Elike%20%3Cem%3Ejaal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekhejri%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekhair%2C%20gumbad%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Eguggul%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20trees%20like%20neem%2C%20peepul%2C%20%3Cem%3Ejamun%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20guava.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20informs%20that%20the%20team%20sources%20the%20saplings%20at%20Rs%202%20from%20the%20state%20government%20nurseries.%20This%20year%2C%20Bheraram%20says%2C%20he%20bought%2028%2C000%20saplings%20to%20plant%20in%20public%20places%20like%20schools%2C%20playgrounds%2C%20and%20crematoriums.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20these%20saplings%20are%20planted%20during%20the%2