0people%20look%20at%20disabilities%20with%20sympathy%20but%20we%20look%20for%20the%20ability%20in%20the%20disability.%20Every%20person%20has%20an%20inner%20potential%20that%20they%20need%20to%20realise%2C%20once%20you%20do%20that%20there%20is%20nothing%20stopping%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20are%20a%20person%20with%20a%20disability%20and%20want%20to%20experience%20adventure%20sports%20with%20Major%20Vivek%2C%20you%20can%20contact%20him%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fclaw.global%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695384120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fclaw-1-1695382576.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D330663%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Major%20Vivek%20Jacob%20took%20early%20retirement%20from%20the%20Army%20and%20started%20CLAW%20Global%20(Conquer%20Land%2C%20Air%2C%20Water)%20%E2%80%94%20a%20social%20impact%20organisation%20that%20is%20helping%20persons%20with%20disabilities%20experience%20adventure%20sports%20like%20scuba%20diving%2C%20sky%20diving%20and%20mountaineering.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Toured%20Across%20India%20To%20Learn%20From%20Farmers%E2%80%99%3A%20How%20a%20Retd%20Colonel%20Found%20Passion%20in%20Orchid%20Farming%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EColonel%20Sujan%20Mohanty%20(57)%2C%20is%20a%20retired%20army%20man%20who%20set%20out%20to%20create%20a%20successful%20life%20for%20himself%20post%20his%20service%20of%2022%20years.%20A%20civil%20engineer%20as%20well%2C%20he%20now%20cultivates%20and%20manages%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%